						.gs-guide__title-label Prerequisites
					.gs-guide__subtitle
						p Before you begin, make sure you have <a href="http://nodejs.org/download" target="_blank">Node.js</a>, <a href="http://www.mongodb.org/downloads" target="_blank">MongoDB</a>, <a href="https://developer.apple.com/xcode/" target="_blank">XCode</a> (for generarting iOS app) and/or the <a href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html" target="_blank">Android SDK</a> (for generarting Android app) installed.
						p You'll need a reasonable working knowledge of Javascript to use LandmarkJS, as well as familiarity with basics such as database concepts, and using node / npm etc.
		
